data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home nestled in the Sandstone Community. This home is accompanied by a large lot with a fenced backyard, a spacious 2 car garage, and features a thoughtfully designed interior with no carpet, offering a mix of sleek sleek tile and LVP flooring throughout. The open concept living areas are perfect for entertaining, while the private bedrooms provide comfort and relaxation. Enjoy the convenience of a like new home offering endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment. This is a must see property for those seeking a blend of style, comfort, and space.
